Demon Encounter closes at 9:00 (GL), 23:00 (CN/TW/GL) and 24:00 (JP).

== Solo Events ==
=== Demon Seal===
A shikigami appears and they can be challenged to give shikigami shards, like regular [[Demon Seal|Demon Seals]], but there is a wider variety of shikigami that can appear (including SSRs).

===Demon Quiz===
:''For more information, visit the [[Answer List|Demon Quiz Answer List]] page.''
A letter appears and has 3 multi-choice questions. Select the correct one to get the shown rewards.

===Demon Chest===
A treasure chest appears and requires 50 Jades to unlock the treasure shown.

