=== Rare Bosses & Ultra Versions===
:''For more information on the individual Rare Bosses, visit the [[Demon Encounter/Boss]] page.''
Rare Bosses are available to all nearby players across the entire server. Bosses are [[Tsuchigumo]], [[Oboroguruma]], [[Gashadokuro (Boss)|Gashadokuro (Odokuro)]], [[Jishin Namazu]], [[Shinkirou]] and [[Kiryou Utahime|Kiryou Utahime (Ghostly Songstress)]]. They take turns being the Rare Boss of Demon Encounter, changing each day. 

Players with the required Achievement Marks can search for and challenge Ultra Bosses. Each player can choose to challenge either a Rare Boss or an Ultra Boss. Ultra Bosses grants better Ranking Rewards than Rare Bosses.

